coverage movement: +19.93 stmts, +16.16 branches, +18.79 funcs, +20.19 lines.\\nRemaining largest gaps stay in very large script surfaces still near 0% (scripts/dogfood-package-first.mjs, scripts/smoke-external-packages.mjs, scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs, scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs, scripts/release/static-quality-gate.mjs, scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs)."
  "2026-06-14T20:29:02.400Z",lane-c-wave3-subagent-20260614,"Wave3 evidence (strict continuation toward literal all-source 100):\n\nCommands run and outcomes:\n1) Bootstrap prerequisite chain:\n   npm install -g . && pm --version && node -v && pnpm -v && pnpm build\n   Result: exit 0 (pm 2026.6.13, node v25.9.0, pnpm 10.33.4, build passed).\n2) Focused lane-c validation:\n   PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave2.spec.ts\n   Result: exit 0; Test Files 1 passed, Tests 24 passed.\n3) Baseline focused probe (before edits):\n   PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage -- --coverage.thresholds.lines=0 --coverage.thresholds.functions=0 --coverage.thresholds.branches=0 --coverage.thresholds.statements=0 tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave2.spec.ts tests/unit/docs-skills-gate.spec.ts tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts\n   Result: exit 0; Test Files 3 passed, Tests 33 passed.\n4) Post-edit focused probe (after edits, same command):\n   PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage -- --coverage.thresholds.lines=0 --coverage.thresholds.functions=0 --coverage.thresholds.branches=0 --coverage.thresholds.statements=0 tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave2.spec.ts tests/unit/docs-skills-gate.spec.ts tests/integration/release-automation-contract.spec.ts\n   Result: exit 0; Test Files 3 passed, Tests 41 passed.\n\nPer-target coverage movement (lines %, branches %):\n- scripts/dogfood-package-first.mjs: 0.00 -> 93.30 lines, 0.00 -> 50.00 branches\n- scripts/release/docs-skills-gate.mjs: 24.40 -> 75.60 lines, 21.11 -> 64.59 branches\n- scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs: 0.00 -> 82.88 lines, 0.00 -> 67.90 branches\n- scripts/release/static-quality-gate.mjs: 0.00 -> 77.41 lines, 0.00 -> 62.14 branches\n- scripts/release/run-release-pipeline.mjs: 0.00 -> 45.85 lines, 0.00 -> 31.06 branches\n- scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs: 0.00 -> 81.53 lines, 0.00 -> 62.50 branches\n- scripts/smoke-external-packages.mjs: 0.00 -> 80.62 lines, 0.00 -> 61.60 branches\n\nScope: expanded tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave2.spec.ts with deterministic mocked coverage for docs-skills gate, static-quality gate, release pipeline, compatibility gate, sentry telemetry gate, smoke-external-packages, and dogfood-package-first orchestrators."
  "2026-06-14T20:40:45.352Z",lane-c-wave4-subagent-20260614,"Wave4 evidence (strict all-source push for currently-zero scripts):\n\nBootstrap + orient + claim:\n- npm install -g . && pm --version && node -v && pnpm -v && pnpm build -> exit 0.\n- export PM_AUTHOR=lane-c-wave4-subagent-20260614.\n- pm context/search/list-open/list-in-progress + pm claim pm-f2ne -> exit 0.\n\nImplemented:\n- Extended tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave2.spec.ts with deterministic branch coverage for:\n  scripts/generate-release-notes.mjs\n  scripts/release/verify-published-release.mjs\n  scripts/smoke-claude-plugin.mjs\n  scripts/smoke-npx-from-pack.mjs\n  scripts/run-tests.mjs\n  scripts/plugin-mcp-smoke-harness.mjs\n  scripts/check-secrets.mjs\n- Added success + failure branch assertions with mocked child_process/fs/readline/plugin harness boundaries.\n\nVerification outcomes:\n1) PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave2.spec.ts\n   -> exit 0; Test Files 1 passed, Tests 32 passed.\n2) Baseline probe (before edits):\n   PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage -- --coverage.thresholds.lines=0 --coverage.thresholds.functions=0 --coverage.thresholds.branches=0 --coverage.thresholds.statements=0 tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave2.spec.ts tests/integration/run-tests-script.integration.spec.ts tests/unit/check-secrets.spec.ts\n   -> exit 0; Test Files 3 passed, Tests 32 passed.\n3) Post-edit probe (same command):\n   -> exit 0; Test Files 3 passed, Tests 40 passed.\n\nTargeted script coverage before -> after (lines %, branches %):\n- scripts/generate-release-notes.mjs: 0.00 -> 49.58 lines, 0.00 -> 25.39 branches\n- scripts/release/verify-published-release.mjs: 0.00 -> 77.27 lines, 0.00 -> 50.74 branches\n- scripts/smoke-claude-plugin.mjs: 0.00 -> 86.30 lines, 0.00 -> 53.57 branches\n- scripts/smoke-npx-from-pack.mjs: 0.00 -> 80.88 lines, 0.00 -> 51.78 branches\n- scripts/run-tests.mjs: 0.00 -> 80.43 lines, 0.00 -> 54.16 branches\n- scripts/plugin-mcp-smoke-harness.mjs: 0.00 -> 88.88 lines, 0.00 -> 77.27 branches\n- scripts/check-secrets.mjs: 0.00 -> 89.65 lines, 0.00 -> 80.00 branches"
  "2026-06-15T03:26:14.349Z",claude-code-agent,"Lane C wave5 (opus orchestration, 2026-06-15): sub-agent lane-c-agent-20260614-opus ran ~40min (146 tool calls), cut off by session-limit pre-documentation. Landed: new tests/unit/lane-c/scripts-wave5.spec.ts (run-gates, release/utils, smoke-claude-plugin, smoke-codex-plugin-mcp, plugin-mcp-smoke-harness, run-tests, smoke-cleanup branches) + modified scripts (check-secrets, check-secrets-lib, contracts-snapshot, finalize-build, gen-package-runtime-loaders, gen-plugin-mcp-wrappers, generate-release-notes, prepare-build-cache, release/run-gates, release/utils) to expose testable functions. Orchestrator fixed 7 cut-off-left broken smoke-claude-plugin tests: query-bust on importRepoModule defeated vi.doMock of the transitive ./plugin-mcp-smoke-harness.mjs import; added importRepoModuleStable (no query) so the mock matches."
  "2026-06-15T14:39:36.108Z",claude-code-agent,"Bug fix (claude-code-agent, 2026-06-15): the migrated tests/unit/scripts/dogfood-package-first.spec.ts had 2 failing tests in the new PM_DOGFOOD_SEMANTIC=1 path. Root cause: the test's semantic spawn-mock matched ALL 'search-advanced' invocations (pmArgs[0]==='search-advanced'), hijacking the main-flow keyword search-advanced probe (which runs before the semantic probe and expects mode=keyword). The script's keyword assertion then threw, so the JSON summary with semantic_dogfood.attempted was never the last log line. Fix: narrowed both override matchers to require --hybrid (the semantic probe's search-advanced call carries --hybrid; the keyword call does not). Verified: 10/10 pass."
